item.title: CVE-2016-9710|2024-08-06T02:59:03.143Z -- ibm -- cognos%20business%20intelligence
item.description: IBM Predictive Solutions Foundation (formerly PMQ) could allow a remote attacker to include arbitrary files. A remote attacker could send a specially-crafted URL to specify a file from the local system, which could allow the attacker to obtain sensitive information. IBM X-Force ID: 119618.
